
What's new in Ambulant Player 1.4.5?
------------------------------------

Changes between 1.4.5 and 1.4.4:
- SMIL 2.1 default backgroundRepeat has been fixed.

Changes between 1.4.4 and 1.4.2:
- SMIL 2.1 has gone to PR (Proposed Recommendation). The main change is
  that some of the DTD URIs have changed slightly.
- Ambulant Player now passes all SMIL 2.1 interoperability tests.

Changes between 1.4.2 and 1.4.1:
- SMIL 2.1 behaviour of backgroundImage and backgroundRepeat has been fixed.

Changes between 1.4 and 1.4.1:
- Mac player didn't support QuickTime playback. Fixed.
- Windows player "Open URL..." did not work. Fixed.

Complete details are in ChangeLog, but here is a quick summary of the
changes between 1.2 and 1.4:

- full SMIL 2.1 RC support
- limited RTSP support
- many bug fixes
- more documentation



